### **2. The Git Ignore (`.gitignore`)**
This prevents temporary files and logs from cluttering your repository.

`nano .gitignore`
```text
# Go binaries and workspace files
atmos-sentinel
go.sum
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Environment and logs
.bash_history
*.log
.DS_Store

# Temporary Termux files
storage/
